《青春創世紀》在发行后获得了乐评的好评。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据11份乐评整理给出65分的评分。<ref name="MC" />

《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的尼爾·麥考密克认为“1世代的那些歌词与分手和对回家之渴望有关的歌曲已经融入了他们略显沧桑的嗓音”，但也指出他们音乐还是像以前一样是“激情迸发、快节奏、优质的流行音樂，有着精美的歌曲結構，抓耳的鉤部和讓电台爆炸式播放的副歌。”<ref name="The Daily Telegraph">{{cite web|last=McCormick|first=Neil|title=Justin Bieber and One Direction's new albums: 'biting the hand that feeds them'|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/one-direction-made-in-the-am-justin-bieber-purpose-review/|publisher=The Daily Telegraph|date=2015-11-09|accessdate=2015-11-10}}</ref>《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》的肯尼斯·帕特里奇给予专辑四星的评分，认为专辑会成为1世代版的《[[艾比路|艾比路]]》。但他批评组合像“[[預製組件|預製]]的21世纪流行乐机器”，粗制滥造“样板情歌，几乎让人感觉不到有什么个性，或看上去超脱成员们真空包装泡泡糖世界的面目”<ref name="Billboard review" />。

《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的编辑羅伯·謝菲爾德认为，《青春創世紀》“就像1世代版本的《[[Let_It_Be|Let It Be]]》，是世界上最大的流行团体在该表达对过去时光的感谢时做出的唱片”。而对于专辑的旋律，他表示专辑“追随了《[[青春午夜場|青春午夜場]]》和《青春第四課》的搖滾氛圍。”<ref name="RS review" />《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的利亞·格林布拉特給予了專輯B級評分。他認為，1世代在這張專輯中“看起來仍未準備發掘他們自己更加成人化的聲音”。<ref name="Entertainment Weekly" />

==商业成绩==
在英国，《青春創世紀》以93,189份首周销量空降[[英國專輯排行榜|英国专辑榜]]冠军，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-direction-vs-justin-bieber-how-this-weeks-album-chart-race-was-won__12061/|title=One Direction vs Justin Bieber: How this week's album chart race was won|last=Talbot|first=Martin|date=2015-11-20|publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=2015-11-20}}</ref>是1世代在当地第4张冠军专辑，在发行时打破了2015年當地銷售最快專輯的记录。<ref>{{cite web|title = One Direction win fastest selling album of 2015 and 4th Number 1|url = http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-direction-win-fastest-selling-album-of-the-year-and-a-fourth-number-1__12057/|website = officialcharts.com|accessdate = 2015-12-15|archive-date = 2018-06-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180613210637/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-direction-win-fastest-selling-album-of-the-year-and-a-fourth-number-1__12057/|dead-url = no}}</ref>专辑发行首周即获得[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]银销售认证。2016年元旦，专辑更以300,000份销量获得了协会白金销售认证。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-direction-win-fastest-selling-album-of-the-year-and-a-fourth-number-1__12057/|title=One Direction win fastest selling album of the year and a fourth Number 1|last=Myers|first=Justin|date=2015-11-22|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613210637/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-direction-win-fastest-selling-album-of-the-year-and-a-fourth-number-1__12057/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在美國，專輯則以402,000份首周銷量空降[[告示牌二百強專輯榜|《告示牌》二百強專輯榜]]亞軍，其首周銷售數字超過了團體的上一張錄音室專輯《[[青春第四課|青春第四課]]》，<ref>{{cite web|title = Does One Direction's 'Midnight Memories' Follow The Boy Band Third-Album Trend? {{!}} Billboard|url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5800882/does-one-directions-midnight-memories-follow-the-boy-band-third|website = Billboard|accessdate = 2015-12-15|archive-date = 2018-06-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614025646/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5800882/does-one-directions-midnight-memories-follow-the-boy-band-third|dead-url = no}}</ref>打破了男子团体销量逐渐下降的常规。<ref>{{cite news|title = Sorry, boy band haters: One Direction seems unstoppable|url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2014/11/18/sorry-boy-band-haters-one-direction-seems-unstoppable/|newspaper = The Washington Post|date = 2014-11-18|access-date = 2015-12-15|issn = 0190-8286|first = Emily|last = Yahr|archive-date = 2018-06-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180613210626/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2014/11/18/sorry-boy-band-haters-one-direction-seems-unstoppable/|dead-url = no}}</ref>截至2016年4月，专辑全美销量已突破1,000,000份。<ref name="RIAA"/>根據[[國際唱片業協會|國際唱片業協會]]的數據，專輯在2015年全球銷量為240萬份，是當年銷量第6高的專輯。<ref name="IFPI2016">{{cite web|title=Global Music Report|url=http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2016.pdf|publisher=[[International_Federation_of_the_Phonographic_Industry|International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]]|date=2016-04-12|accessdate=2016-04-12|format=PDF|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160730180434/http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2016.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

